mailSender::addCC()

Description
    public bool mailSender::addCC(string $address [, string $name = ''])
	Adds the address/name pair to the array, $this->cc[].
	  
Parameters
    address
		The e-mail address of the recipient.
    name
		An optional parameter.  The name associated with the recipient's e-mail address.  Default value is ''.
Return Values
    Returns TRUE upon success.  Returns FALSE otherwise.
    
See Also
	mailSender::addAttachment()
    mailSender::addBCC()
    mailSender::addBody()
    mailSender::addRecipient()
    mailSender::addReplyTo()
	mailSender::addSender()
	mailSender::addSubject()